org.zend.webapi.internal.core.connection.request
Class MultipartRepresentation

java.lang.Object
  OutputRepresentation
      org.zend.webapi.internal.core.connection.request.MultipartRepresentation

public class MultipartRepresentation
extends OutputRepresentation

Defines the multipart/form- data, which can be used by a wide variety of applications and transported by a wide variety of protocols as a way of returning a set of values as the result of a user filling out a form.

Author:
Roy, 2011
See Also:
http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc2388.txt
